long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Struggling to navigate the complexities of manually combining classes without conflicts? AMIS Schedule Unitizer removes all the guesswork for you!

Simply specify the classes you're eyeing for the semester, and AMISSU will craft a schedule of classes that you can take altogether!
